snippet.title: Ambulance Life: A Paramedic Simulator | Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Ambulance Life: A Paramedic Simulator will be available on PC, PlayStation®5 and Xbox Series X|S on February 6th, 2025! 

No day is like the other.

In Ambulance Life: A Paramedic Simulator, you’ll face intense scenarios, provide critical care to shocked victims, and manage the pressure of life-saving missions. Keep your cool, use your skills to diagnose patients, and deliver the best medical aid possible.

Preorder are available now: 
PlayStation : WIP
Xbox : WIP

Follow us on Twitter: https://x.com/TheAmbulanceSim

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1926520/Ambulance_Life_A_Paramedic_Simulator/
